I found two namespace-related problems:

1. The `record` element is in no namespace. Therefore, you need to change

        if elem.tag == &#39;{http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/}record&#39;:

   to

        if elem.tag == &#39;record&#39;:

2. `elem.find(&#39;{http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/}dc:identifier&#39;)` is not correct. The `dc:` bit must be removed.

